des:
Ask for Developer Facts, and learn about what coders need to know.

Developer Facts is guaranteed to make you smarter as a developer.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Developer Facts" or "Alexa, open Developer Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
